      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "FOREGROUND OPTION"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The foreground processing option permits execution of a program from"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "within SPF/PC."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The foreground selection panel, which is displayed when option 4 is"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "entered on the primary option panel, allows you to select one of the"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "programs listed on the panel, or to modify the contents of the panel."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Items on the foreground selection panel may also be invoked from any"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "SPF/PC panel by the USER <option name> primary command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "The following topic will be presented only if selected by number:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1 + Editing the Foreground Selection Panel"
      },
